어 있는 node_modules…","fields":{"slug":"/주저리주저리/dependenciesVSdevDependencies/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"November 21, 2022","title":"dependencies vs devDependencies","description":"package.json의 dependencies vs devDependencies 속성에 대하여","tags":["node"],"thumbnailImg":null}},{"excerpt":"This is my first post on my new fake blog! How exciting! I'm sure I'll write a lot mo re interesting things in the future. Oh, and here's a…","fields":{"slug":"/hello-world/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"May 01, 2015","title":"Hello World","description":"Hello World","tags":null,"thumbnailImg":null}}]},"markdownRemark":{"id":"f5c06fd0-2307-55ab-8a17-ec71720144ad","excerpt":"React 프로젝트 생성하기 제일 먼저 recoil을 사용하게 될 프로젝트를 생성해줍니다.  Recoil 기본 - 문자열 카운터 예제 recoil 설치하기\n터미널에서 다음 명령어를 입력하여 recoil 패키지를 설치합니다. <RecoilRoot> 태그\n가장 상위 컴포넌트인 App.jsx…","html":"<h3>React 프로젝트 생성하기</h3>\n<p>제일 먼저 recoil을 사용하게 될 프로젝트를 생성해줍니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npx create-react-app [프로젝트명]</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/604580767068bbd04c5d29324225a32d/30c92/create_react.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.86075949367089%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"react 프로젝트 설치\"\n        title=\"react 프로젝트 설치\"\n        src=\"/static/604580767068bbd04c5d29324225a32d/f058b/create_react.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/604580767068bbd04c5d29324225a32d/c26ae/create_react.png 158w,\n/static/604580767068bbd04c5d29324225a32d/6bdcf/create_react.png 315w,\n/static/604580767068bbd04c5d29324225a32d/f058b/create_react.png 630w,\n/static/604580767068bbd04c5d29324225a32d/30c92/create_react.png 874w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Recoil 기본 - 문자열 카운터 예제</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>recoil 설치하기\n터미널에서 다음 명령어를 입력하여 recoil 패키지를 설치합니다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install recoil</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>&#x3C;RecoilRoot> 태그\n가장 상위 컴포넌트인 App.jsx에 다음과 같이 &#x3C;RecoilRoot> 태그로 컴포넌트를 둘러싸줍니다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>⭐CharacterCounter 컴포넌트는 이 다음 문단에서 만들 컴포넌트입니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">//App.jsx</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> RecoilRoot <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"recoil\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> CharacterCounter <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./CharacterCounter\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>RecoilRoot<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>CharacterCounter <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>RecoilRoot<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> App</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>CharacterCounter 컴포넌트</li>\n</ol>\n<p>컴포넌트의 기본 뼈대는 다음과 같습니다. 상태 관리를 위해 recoil에서 몇몇 속성을 import하였습니다.</p>\n<p>&#x3C;TextInput/>과 &#x3C;CharacterCount/>는 뒤에서 구현할 것입니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">//CharacterCounter.jsx</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> atom<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> selector<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> useRecoilState<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> useRecoilValue <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"recoil\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">CharacterCounter</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>TextInput <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>CharacterCount <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> CharacterCounter</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>atom</li>\n</ul>\n<p>atom이란 recoil에서 전역상태의 데이터를 저장하는 기본 단위입다.</p>\n<p>동일한 atom을 사용하는 컴포넌트는 해당 atom의 data, 즉 상태를 공유합니다.\nkey 속성의 값은 전역 상태의 이름을 의미합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> textState <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">atom</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">key</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"textState\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//전역 상태의 이름</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>atom의 사용 - useRecoilState()</li>\n</ul>\n<p>react의 useState 함수와 동일하게 사용할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>+추가 : 위 속성을 별개의 값으로 추출할 수 있다.</p>\n<p>useRecoilValue : atom의 값을 불러온다.</p>\n<p>useSetRecoilValue : atom의 값을 설정한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">TextInput</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setText<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useRecoilState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>textState<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//전역 상태를 읽고 수정한다</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">onChange</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">e</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">setText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>input type<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"text\"</span> value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> onChange<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>onChange<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>br <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">Echo</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>selector\natom의 state로부터 파생되는 데이터를 저장할 수 있게 해줍니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>selector를 사용하면 최소한의 상태집합만 atom에 저장하고, state로부터 파생된 데이터(ex : text의 길이, 숫자의 짝/홀수 여부)는 selector에 명시한 함수를 통해 추출함으로서 불필요한 상태의 보존을 방지할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> charCountState <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">selector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">key</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"charCountState\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">get</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> get <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> text <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>textState<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> text<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">CharacterCount</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> count <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useRecoilValue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>charCountState<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//charCountState 값을 읽는다.</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Character Count<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>count<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>local storage에 상태 저장하기</h3>\n<p>이렇게 생성된 전역변수는 웹 페이지를 새로고침할 경우 초기화됩니다. 만약 새로고침 하더라도 설정된 전역변수 값을 유지하고자 한다면, 브라우저의 local storage에 값을 저장하여 불러오게 하면 됩니다.</p>\n<p>터미널에서 다음 명령어를 입력하여 recoil-persist 패키지를 설치합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install recoil-persist</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> recoilPersist <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"recoil-persist\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> persistAtom <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">recoilPersist</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">key</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"textState\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//local storage에 해당 값을 저장하고 불러올 수 있도록 설정</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> textState <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">atom</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">key</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"textState\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//전역 상태의 이름</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">effects_UNSTABLE</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>persistAtom<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//recoil-persist 적용</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e00160c174e003ce36a8ccbe7bd87eaa/d326d/recoil.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.92405063291139%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"local storage에 저장된 결과\"\n        title=\"local storage에 저장된 결과\"\n        src=\"/static/e00160c174e003ce36a8ccbe7bd87eaa/f058b/recoil.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e00160c174e003ce36a8ccbe7bd87eaa/c26ae/recoil.png 158w,\n/static/e00160c174e003ce36a8ccbe7bd87eaa/6bdcf/recoil.png 315w,\n/static/e00160c174e003ce36a8ccbe7bd87eaa/f058b/recoil.png 630w,\n/static/e00160c174e003ce36a8ccbe7bd87eaa/40601/recoil.png 945w,\n/static/e00160c174e003ce36a8ccbe7bd87eaa/d326d/recoil.png 1197w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>참고 게시글</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://recoiljs.org/ko/docs/introduction/getting-started/\">Recoil 시작하기</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://velog.io/@tchaikovsky/Recoil-persist%EB%A1%9C-state%EB%A5%BC-localstorage%EB%A1%9C-%EC%A0%80%EC%9E%A5%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">Recoil-persist로 state를 localstorage로 저장하기</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Recoil 사용하기","date":"2022년 11월 30일","description":"Recoil 기본 및 로컬 스토리지 사용하기","tags":["recoil","frontend","상태관리 라이브러리"]}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/데이터베이스/데이터베이스 정규화/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"데이터베이스 정규화 - 1"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/데이터베이스/데이터베이스 정규화 - 2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"데이터베이스 정규화 - 2"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"f5c06fd0-2307-55ab-8a17-ec71720144ad","previousPostId":"0e5ae450-3fe1-5c70-a762-f02a24516a8f","nextPostId":"807b5367-e197-5888-a026-b23c7de43a4c"}},"staticQueryHashes":["230163734","2841359383"],"slicesMap":{}}